OL,3,C'Miscarriage of justice' fears over
OL,4,Cbrother and sister's deaths in
OL,5,CPembrokeshire
OL,7,FNew questions are being raised about
OL,8,Fthe 1976 deaths of a brother and
OL,9,Fsister who were found dead in their
OL,10,Ffarmhouse in Llangolman, Pembrokeshire.
OL,12,FAt the time, Dyfed-Powys Police
OL,13,Fconcluded that Martha Thomas - known
OL,14,Fas Patti - was killed by her brother,
OL,15,FGriff, and that he died as a result of
OL,16,Fa fire he lit in the house.
