OL,3,C'Miscarriage of justice' fears over
OL,4,Cbrother and sister's deaths in
OL,5,CPembrokeshire
OL,7,FIn a special episode of Y Byd ar
OL,8,FBedwar on S4C, two experts in
OL,9,Fhistorical cases claim there is room
OL,10,Ffor suspicion that someone else could
OL,11,Fbe responsible for their deaths,
OL,12,Fraising the question that Griff Thomas
OL,13,Fmay have been wrongly blamed for
OL,14,Fkilling his sister.
OL,16,FFor decades, relatives and those who
OL,17,Fknew them well have also insisted that
OL,18,FGriff could not have killed his sister
OL,19,Fand that someone else was responsible.
