OL,3,C'Miscarriage of justice' fears over
OL,4,Cbrother and sister's deaths in
OL,5,CPembrokeshire
OL,7,FAn open verdict was reached regarding
OL,8,Fthe death of Griff Thomas, but police
OL,9,Fbelieved he died after setting himself
OL,10,Fon fire.
OL,12,FProfessor Niamh Nic Daed, head of the
OL,13,Fforensic department at the University
OL,14,Fof Dundee and one of the expert
OL,15,Fwitnesses in the Grenfell Tower Fire
OL,16,FInquiry, said she has never
OL,17,Fencountered a similar case before.
OL,19,F"There were no ignitable liquids or
OL,20,Fliquid accelerants like petrol or
OL,21,Fparaffin or whatever used," she said.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/11
