OL,7,F"So the most likely cause of the fire
OL,8,Fwas somebody deliberately setting fire
OL,9,Fto the combustible materials that were
OL,10,Fpresent. You then need to think about
OL,11,Fusing your experience to determine
OL,12,Fwhether that type of fire would be
OL,13,Flikely to be self-inflicted."
