OL,3,C'Miscarriage of justice' fears over
OL,4,Cbrother and sister's deaths in
OL,5,CPembrokeshire
OL,7,FAfter reading the Dyfed-Powys Police
OL,8,Freport from 1976 on the investigation
OL,9,Finto the Thomas family's deaths,
OL,10,FProfessor Nic Daeid believes important
OL,11,Fquestions arise, saying: "It certainly
OL,12,Fsuggests to me that there are
OL,13,Fquestions with regard to whether the
OL,14,Ffire was deliberately set by Griff, or
OL,15,Fwhether it was the action of another
OL,16,Fperson."
