OL,3,C'Miscarriage of justice' fears over
OL,4,Cbrother and sister's deaths in
OL,5,CPembrokeshire
OL,7,F"That, I don't think is right. I think
OL,8,Fit is very possible it is a
OL,9,Fmiscarriage of justice and I think it
OL,10,Fis only right for at least an inquest
OL,11,Fto explore those factors."
OL,13,FThe programme also hears from
OL,14,Frelatives of Griff and Patti Thomas,
OL,15,Fwho have been fighting for decades to
OL,16,Fclear their brother's name.
OL,18,F"My father, from the beginning, said
OL,19,Fthat the story wasn't right," says Huw.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/11
