OL,3,C'Miscarriage of justice' fears over
OL,4,Cbrother and sister's deaths in
OL,5,CPembrokeshire
OL,7,F"It was just the two of them. Neither
OL,8,Fwould ever have harmed the other,
OL,9,Fnever.
OL,11,F"I was 15 at the time and I'm 63 now,
OL,12,Fwho's going to fight on after my day?
OL,13,FI feel deeply about the injustice of
OL,14,Fthe whole thing."
OL,16,FIn October 2022, Dyfed-Powys Police
OL,17,Fannounced it was conducting a forensic
OL,18,Freview of material which had been kept
OL,19,Ffrom the original investigation in
OL,20,F1976.
